snippet.title: IMMORTAL SAGA - TRAILER
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD IMMORTAL SAGA : https://starmongoose.itch.io/immortal-saga

Immortal Saga is my own little game I started making when quarantine first began a year ago. It's a Fire Emblem style game and features a cast of characters that comprise of my friends and community. Thank you so much everyone for showing this support.

I'll link the game here when it's out!
